Class ValidatorConstants

java.lang.Object
  oracle.apps.fnd.applcore.trees.validator.util.ValidatorConstants

public final class ValidatorConstants
extends java.lang.Object

Constants used for Tree Management Audit Validators. Generic (utility) constants and functions. Other generic utility functions should be included here. All methods and members are static and do not need an instance of the class to use the methods.
